This simulation models a conversation in which the patient with senility has a chance of "forgetting" a word. The act of forgetting is modeled with a filter that makes her unable to speak with certain probability.

This simulation models a set of movements that the patient has difficulty performing . For this we created a filter in which the acts of walking, sitting and gettin in and out of bed are delayed by a percentage.

This simulation models the situation in which the patient sometimes forgets what is she doing. For this we created a filter in which the task she is about to perform is replaced by another one in which she talks aloud.
